Germany’s Roesler Aims for Tax Reduction, WirtschaftsWoche Says

-- B y   C h r i s t i a n   V i t s
-- 
2011-06-04T09:48:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-04/germany-s-roesler-aims-for-tax-reduction-wirtschaftswoche-says.html
Philipp Roesler,  Germany ’s new
economy minister, wants to reduce the burden on taxpayers as the
country’s economy recovers,  WirtschaftsWoche  reported, citing an
interview.  Roesler also called for a reduction in the amount of new
debt Germany takes on, according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
